lop and empower yourselves plus you will be joining a community who understand the importance of knowledge sharing, mentoring and being mentored.\u00a0", "Our large team of engineers, developers and architects is being forged from a need to create a real Digital Transformation throughout our European markets bringing in AI assistants, advanced consumer analytics and upgraded online consumer journey solutions among others. It is an exciting time for Electrolux and our team is right in the middle of things.\u00a0", "We are trying to build something here: a culture of excellence, freedom of expression, innovation and a stimulating, enjoyable work environment. We really mean it!"], "people": ["https://stackoverflow.com/users/16106584/jason-benskin?tab=profile", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/2471322/ales?tab=profile", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/story/16106609", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/14888246/bogdan-nikolaev?tab=profile", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/8757882/daniil-kunin?tab=profile", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/16106710/anastasia-shatskaya?tab=profile", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/16107631/mariia-khan?tab=profile", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3532995/user3532995?tab=profile", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/story/2442831", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/story/880395", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/story/16113768", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/473904/valentino-dellaica?tab=profile", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/15394969/drumfire?tab=profile", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/5364142/b-random?tab=profile", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/14570112/vitaly-verkash?tab=profile", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/16046242/anton-mukhin?tab=profile", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/16115993/robert-lamb?tab=profile", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/story/16117435", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1527997/aprian-diaz-novandi?tab=profile", "https://stackoverflow.com/users/16301559/emanuele-degano?tab=profile", "https://stackove